		{"id":"stats-endpoint-node","type":"text","text":"## 📊 Stats & Monitoring\n\n**/stats/performance** | **/stats/agents** | **/health**\n\nMetrics, latency, uptime","x":320,"y":340,"width":930,"height":180,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"vcenter-server-node","type":"text","text":"## 🌐 vCenter Server\n\n**VMware vCenter 7.0+**\n\n- VM inventory management\n- ESXi host orchestration\n- Resource pools\n- Datastores\n- Networks\n\n**API:** pyvmomi (Python SDK)","x":-380,"y":3680,"width":500,"height":280,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"config-files-node","type":"text","text":"## ⚙️ Configuration Files\n\n**config.json** (vCenter creds, RAG v2.4) | **agents.yaml** (routing keywords) | **logging_config.json** (log paths)","x":-380,"y":4020,"width":1000,"height":180,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"documents-node","type":"text","text":"## 📚 Document Repository\n\n**documents/** → PDF/MD/TXT files organized by folders (vcenter, esxi, gtr, dvd, dns, etc.)\n\n**Indexed:** ChromaDB + BM25 for hybrid search","x":670,"y":4020,"width":900,"height":180,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"chromadb-node","type":"text","text":"## 🗄️ ChromaDB\n\n**Vector Store**\n\n- Path: data/chroma_db\n- Documents: PDF, MD, TXT\n- Chunk size: 1400 chars\n- Overlap: 350 chars\n- Embeddings: nomic-embed-text\n\n**Metadata:** filename, folder, chunk_id","x":-2700,"y":3580,"width":440,"height":280,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"bm25-node","type":"text","text":"## 📑 BM25 Index\n\n**Keyword Search**\n\n- k1=1.5, b=0.75\n- Index: page_content + filename + headers\n- Spanish stopwords (23)\n- Filler phrase removal (12 patterns)\n\n**Hybrid α:** 0.35-0.70 adaptive","x":-2210,"y":3580,"width":440,"height":280,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"sqlite-node","type":"text","text":"## 💾 SQLite Databases\n\n**auth.db:**\n- users (username, password_hash, role)\n- sessions\n- RBAC: user/admin/superuser\n\n**users.db:**\n- Per-agent sessions\n- Conversation history\n- User preferences","x":-1720,"y":3580,"width":440,"height":280,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"logs-node","type":"text","text":"## 📋 Structured Logs\n\n**6 Categories (JSON):**\n\n1. **api.log** - HTTP requests\n2. **business.log** - vCenter operations\n3. **security.log** - Auth events\n4. **audit.log** - User actions\n5. **performance.log** - Metrics, latency\n6. **system.log** - Errors, exceptions\n\n**RAG:** retrieval_metrics.jsonl","x":-1270,"y":3580,"width":440,"height":280,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"cisco-node","type":"text","text":"## 🔌 Cisco Catalyst\n\n**Network Switch**\n\n- Port statistics\n- VLAN management\n- SNMP v2c metrics\n\n**Monitoring:** 5min intervals","x":1350,"y":3680,"width":400,"height":280,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"truenas-node","type":"text","text":"## 💿 TrueNAS NAS\n\n**Storage Backend**\n\n- NFS datastores\n- Backup storage\n- SNMP v3 metrics\n\n**Monitoring:** 5min intervals","x":900,"y":3680,"width":400,"height":280,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"esxi-hosts-node","type":"text","text":"## 🖥️ ESXi Hosts\n\n**Hypervisors**\n\n- VM execution\n- Resource allocation\n- SNMP monitoring\n- Performance metrics\n\n**Protocol:** vSphere API","x":395,"y":3680,"width":450,"height":280,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"reranker-node","type":"text","text":"## 🎯 Reranker\n\n**Heuristic scoring:**\n- 25% original similarity\n- 40% term frequency\n- 15% length penalty\n- 10% position bonus\n- +75% internal docs boost","x":-1720,"y":4020,"width":440,"height":220,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"embedding-cache-node","type":"text","text":"## 💨 Embedding Cache\n\n**LRU Cache:**\n- Size: 1000 queries\n- Hit rate: ~30% speedup\n- Persistent across restarts\n\n**Metrics:** hit/miss tracking","x":-2210,"y":4020,"width":440,"height":220,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"query-expander-node","type":"text","text":"## 🔍 Query Expander\n\n**62 Term Families:**\n- VMware basics (12)\n- Infrastructure (4)\n- HA/Performance (4)\n- Storage (3)\n- Project tools (11)\n- Bidirectional mapping","x":-2700,"y":4020,"width":440,"height":220,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"search-modes-node","type":"text","text":"## 🔎 Search Modes\n\n1. **Strict:** \"SOLO vcenter\" → only vcenter folder\n2. **Boosting:** \"busca en esxi\" → x2 esxi docs\n3. **Global:** Default across all docs\n\n**Folder filtering:** Pre/post retrieval","x":-1270,"y":4020,"width":440,"height":220,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"tech-stack-node","type":"text","text":"## 🛠️ Technology Stack\n\n### Backend Framework\n- **Flask 2.0+** - Web server\n- **LangChain** - Agent framework\n- **LangChain-Ollama** - LLM integration\n- **pyvmomi** - VMware SDK\n\n### AI/LLM\n- **Ollama** - Local LLM runtime (localhost:11434)\n- **gpt-oss:20b** - Executor model (reasoning)\n- **nomic-embed-text** - Embeddings (768 dim)\n\n### Storage\n- **ChromaDB** - Vector database\n- **SQLite** - Auth & sessions (auth.db, users.db)\n- **BM25** - Keyword index (in-memory)\n\n### RAG Components\n- **langchain_text_splitters** - Semantic chunking\n- **pypdf** - PDF parsing\n- **rank_bm25** - BM25 implementation\n\n### Monitoring\n- **APScheduler** - Background jobs\n- **pysnmp** - SNMP collectors (v2c, v3)\n- **Structured logging** - JSON logs\n\n### Security\n- **bcrypt** - Password hashing\n- **Flask sessions** - Session management\n- **RBAC** - Role-based access control\n\n### Dependencies\n- Python 3.9+\n- VMware vCenter 7.0+\n- Ollama with models downloaded\n- SNMP-enabled devices (optional)","x":3680,"y":3180,"width":900,"height":500,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"key-features-node","type":"text","text":"## ✨ Key Features & Design Patterns\n\n### 1. Dual-Model Optimization\n- **Formatter:** gpt-oss:20b (optional) - Query cleaning\n- **Executor:** gpt-oss:20b - Reasoning & tool selection\n- **Benefit:** Better accuracy with pre-processed queries\n\n### 2. Per-User Isolation\n- Each user has separate `ConversationBufferMemory`\n- Stored in `user_memories{}` dict\n- Prevents context bleeding\n\n### 3. Sticky Routing (180s)\n- Track last agent per user\n- Auto-route follow-ups without re-classification\n- Example: \"Lista VMs\" → vCenter, then \"solo las apagadas\" → vCenter\n\n### 4. MCP Security Pattern\n- ALL vCenter tools through MCP server\n- No direct pyvmomi calls from agents\n- Centralized security controls\n- Tool registry audit trail\n\n### 5. Connection Pooling\n- Max 5 vCenter connections\n- 30s idle timeout\n- Per-user session reuse\n- Prevents session exhaustion\n\n### 6. Hybrid RAG\n- Vector (semantic) + BM25 (keyword)\n- Adaptive alpha based on query length\n- Internal docs boost (+75% for .md)\n- Query expansion (62 families)\n\n### 7. Structured Logging\n- JSON format across 6 categories\n- Context managers for auto-logging\n- Metrics tracking\n- Easy parsing for monitoring tools","x":3680,"y":2600,"width":900,"height":500,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"background-agents-detail","type":"text","text":"## ⏰ Background Agents Detail\n\n### 1. Daily vCenter Report\n**Schedule:** 10:30 daily\n- VM inventory snapshot\n- Resource usage summary\n- Alert collection\n- PDF generation\n**Output:** reports/daily_YYYY-MM-DD.pdf\n\n### 2. Weekly vCenter Report\n**Schedule:** Mondays 11:00\n- Week-over-week comparison\n- Trend analysis\n- Capacity planning data\n**Output:** reports/weekly_YYYY-WW.pdf\n\n### 3. SNMP TrueNAS Collector\n**Schedule:** Every 5 minutes\n- Storage metrics (used, free, total)\n- Disk health status\n- RAID status\n**Protocol:** SNMPv3\n**Storage:** metrics/truenas.jsonl\n\n### 4. SNMP Switch Collector\n**Schedule:** Every 5 minutes\n- Port statistics (in/out)\n- Errors, drops\n- VLAN info\n**Protocol:** SNMPv2c\n**Storage:** metrics/switch.jsonl\n\n### 5. ESXi Collector\n**Schedule:** Every 10 minutes\n- CPU, memory, storage per host\n- VM count, power state distribution\n**API:** vSphere API via pyvmomi\n**Storage:** metrics/esxi.jsonl\n\n### 6. Database Cleanup\n**Schedule:** Daily 02:00\n- Old session cleanup\n- Log rotation\n- Metrics pruning (>7 days)","x":3680,"y":1980,"width":900,"height":550,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"monitoring-detail","type":"text","text":"## 📊 Monitoring & Observability\n\n### Structured Logging (6 Categories)\n\n**1. api.log** (HTTP Layer)\n- Endpoint calls, status codes\n- Request/response payloads\n- Client info\n\n**2. business.log** (Business Operations)\n- VM deployments, snapshots\n- vCenter operations\n- Success/failure metrics\n\n**3. security.log** (Security Events)\n- Login attempts (success/fail)\n- RBAC violations\n- Session management\n\n**4. audit.log** (User Actions)\n- Who did what when\n- Query history\n- Admin actions\n\n**5. performance.log** (Performance Metrics)\n- Latency per operation\n- Agent response times\n- Resource usage\n\n**6. system.log** (System Errors)\n- Exceptions, stack traces\n- Connection failures\n- Configuration issues\n\n### RAG Metrics\n**retrieval_metrics.jsonl:**\n- Query text\n- Search mode\n- Retrieval scores\n- Latency\n- Documents returned","x":3680,"y":1400,"width":900,"height":500,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"security-detail","type":"text","text":"## 🔐 Security & Authentication\n\n### Authentication Flow\n1. User submits credentials → **/login**\n2. Bcrypt hash verification (auth.db)\n3. Session creation (Flask sessions + SQLite)\n4. RBAC check (user/admin/superuser)\n\n### Protected Routes\n- `@authenticated_action` decorator\n- Auto-checks session['username']\n- Logs to security.log\n\n### Session Management\n**Dual System:**\n1. **ACTIVE_SESSIONS** (in-memory, 3600s timeout)\n2. **SQLite users.db** (persistent, per-agent)\n\n### Rate Limiting\n- Login attempts throttling\n- API request limits per user\n- Configurable thresholds\n\n### Default Users\n- admin/admin (role: admin)\n- user/user (role: user)\n- Passwords: bcrypt hashed in auth.db","x":3680,"y":870,"width":900,"height":450,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"rag-pipeline-detail","type":"text","text":"## 📚 RAG v2.4 Pipeline (8-Stage)\n\n### Stage 1: Search Mode Detection\n- **Strict:** \"SOLO vcenter\" → only vcenter folder\n- **Boosting:** \"busca en esxi\" → prioritize esxi\n- **Global:** Default across all documents\n\n### Stage 2: Query Normalization\n- Remove Spanish stopwords (23 terms)\n- Remove filler phrases (12 patterns)\n- Clean punctuation\n\n### Stage 3: Query Expansion\n- 62 semantic term families\n- Bidirectional mapping\n- VMware + project-specific terms\n\n### Stage 4: Hybrid Retrieval\n- **Vector Search:** ChromaDB (nomic-embed-text)\n- **Keyword Search:** BM25 (k1=1.5, b=0.75)\n- **Score Normalization:** [0,1]\n- **Adaptive Alpha:** Short query (α=0.35), Long (α=0.70)\n- **Internal Boost:** +75% for .md files\n- **Candidates:** k=40\n\n### Stage 5: Folder Filtering\n- Strict: Keep only target folder\n- Boosting: x2 score for target\n- Global: No filtering\n\n### Stage 6: Reranking\n- Top 40 → 12 documents\n- Scoring: 25% similarity + 40% term_freq + 15% length + 10% position\n\n### Stage 7: Metrics Logging\n- Log to retrieval_metrics.jsonl\n- Query, mode, scores, latency\n\n### Stage 8: LLM Synthesis\n- gpt-oss:20b (num_ctx=16384, temp=0.1)\n- Generate factual response","x":3680,"y":75,"width":900,"height":700,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"classifier-layers-detail","type":"text","text":"## 📌 Classifier 4-Layer System\n\n### Layer 0: Exclusive Keywords\n**agents.yaml** - Fast keyword match\n- \"manual\", \"documentación\" → documentation\n- \"vm\", \"snapshot\" → vcenter\n**Exit rate:** ~40%\n\n### Layer 1: Critical Regex\nHigh-confidence patterns\n- r'\\bcrea.*\\b(?:mcu|eqsim)\\b' → vcenter\n- r'\\bcómo.*\\b(?:configurar|instalar)\\b' → documentation\n**Exit rate:** ~25%\n\n### Layer 2: Intent Detection\nImperative vs learning question\n- Imperative (\"despliega\", \"apaga\") → vcenter\n- Learning (\"qué es\", \"cómo funciona\") → documentation\n**Exit rate:** ~20%\n\n### Layer 3: Weighted Scoring\nKeyword scoring with delta threshold\n- score_vcenter vs score_doc\n- Minimum delta: 0.3\n**Exit rate:** ~10%\n\n### Layer 4: LLM Fallback\nLast resort for ambiguous queries\n- LLM classification prompt\n- Heuristic safety net if LLM fails\n**Exit rate:** ~5%","x":3680,"y":-560,"width":900,"height":550,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"data-flow-title","type":"text","text":"# 🔄 Data Flow Summary\n\n**User Query → Orchestrator → Classifier (4-layer) → Specialized Agent → Tools/RAG → Response**","x":3680,"y":-840,"width":900,"height":200,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"main-agent-node","type":"text","text":"## 🤖 Orquestador\n\n**main_agent.py**\n\n- Entry point\n- chat_api()\n- Agent routing\n- Response aggregation\n- Session tracking","x":1410,"y":800,"width":400,"height":240,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"mcp-registry-node","type":"text","text":"## 🔧 MCPToolRegistry\n\n**mcp_tool_registry.py**\n\n**32 Tools in 8 Groups:**\n\n1. **VM Lifecycle** (5): deploy, power, clone, delete, reconfigure\n2. **Snapshots** (4): create, list, revert, delete\n3. **Info & Monitoring** (6): list_vms, get_vm_info, host_info, resource_usage\n4. **Datastores** (3): list, info, capacity\n5. **Networks** (3): list, attach, detach\n6. **Advanced** (4): migrate, vmotion, set_cpu, set_memory\n7. **Batch** (3): bulk_power, multi_snapshot\n8. **Reports** (4): inventory, performance, alerts\n\n**Security:** ALL tools go through MCP (no direct pyvmomi)","x":-2220,"y":2000,"width":950,"height":280,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"connection-pool-node","type":"text","text":"## 🔌 VCenterConnectionPool\n\n**vcenter_tools.py**\n\n```python\nclass VCenterConnectionPool:\n    max_connections = 5\n    timeout = 30s\n    \n    get_user_si(username)\n    → SmartConnect to vCenter\n    → Reuse if exists\n    → Create if available\n```\n\n**Benefits:**\n- Prevents session exhaustion\n- Per-user isolation\n- Auto-cleanup idle connections\n- Thread-safe with locks\n\n**Monitoring:** connection_pool_size metric","x":-2220,"y":2340,"width":950,"height":220,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"vcenter-agent-node","type":"text","text":"## 🖥️ vCenter Agent\n\n**agent.py**\n\n**Capabilities:**\n- VM operations (deploy, power, clone)\n- Snapshot management\n- Datastore queries\n- Host ESXi info\n- Resource allocation\n\n**Tools:** 29 MCP tools\n**LLM:** gpt-oss:20b executor\n**Memory:** Per-user ConversationBufferMemory","x":-30,"y":2000,"width":600,"height":340,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"background-agents-node","type":"text","text":"## ⏰ Background Agents\n\n**6 Autonomous Agents:**\n\n1. **Daily Report** (10:30) - vCenter inventory\n2. **Weekly Report** (Mondays 11:00)\n3. **SNMP Collector** (5min) - TrueNAS metrics\n4. **Switch Collector** (5min) - Cisco Catalyst\n5. **ESXi Collector** (10min) - Host stats\n6. **Database Cleanup** (Daily 02:00)\n\n**Framework:** APScheduler","x":1860,"y":2000,"width":600,"height":340,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"doc-agent-node","type":"text","text":"## 📚 Documentation Consultant\n\n**doc_consultant.py**\n\n**RAG v2.4 Pipeline (8-stage):**\n1. Search mode detection (strict/boost/global)\n2. Query normalization\n3. Query expansion (62 terms)\n4. Hybrid retrieval (ChromaDB + BM25)\n5. Folder filtering\n6. Reranking (top 8)\n7. Metrics logging\n8. LLM response\n\n**Embeddings:** nomic-embed-text","x":950,"y":2000,"width":600,"height":340,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"doc-agent-details","type":"text","text":"### Doc Agent Flow:\n\n1. Detect search mode (SOLO/busca en)\n2. Expand query (62 semantic families)\n3. Hybrid search (α=0.5 adaptive)\n4. Folder filter (strict/boost)\n5. Rerank top 40 → 12 docs\n6. LLM synthesis (num_ctx=16384)\n\n**Cache:** 1000 query LRU (~30% speedup)","x":2560,"y":2000,"width":600,"height":140,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"vcenter-agent-details","type":"text","text":"### vCenter Agent Flow:\n\n1. `get_user_context()` → Load/create executor\n2. LLM analyzes query → Select MCP tool\n3. `AgentExecutor.invoke()` → Execute\n4. `ConversationBufferMemory.save()`\n5. Return structured response\n\n**Context:** Per-user isolation\n**Timeout:** 30s per operation","x":2560,"y":2200,"width":600,"height":140,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"web-ui-node","type":"text","text":"## 🌐 Web Interface\n\n**orchestrator_chat_auth.html**\n\n- Chat UI\n- Temas claro/oscuro\n- Markdown rendering","x":150,"y":-760,"width":360,"height":320,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"css-themes-node","type":"text","text":"## 🎨 Styles\n\n- Light/Dark themes\n- Responsive design\n- Chat bubbles","x":1290,"y":-760,"width":360,"height":320,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"client-js-node","type":"text","text":"## ⚙️ Client Logic\n\n**orchestrator_chat_auth.js**\n\n- POST /chat requests\n- Session management\n- Response handling","x":790,"y":-760,"width":360,"height":320,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"chat-endpoint-node","type":"text","text":"## 💬 Chat API\n\n**/chat**\n**/chat/stream**\n\n- Query routing\n- User context","x":1110,"y":60,"width":280,"height":220,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"vcenter-api-node","type":"text","text":"## 🖥️ vCenter Direct\n\n**/vcenter/***\n\n- list_vms\n- get_vm_info\n- Direct access","x":490,"y":60,"width":280,"height":220,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"admin-endpoint-node","type":"text","text":"## 👑 Admin\n\n**/admin/users**\n**/admin/roles**\n\n- User mgmt\n- Stats","x":800,"y":60,"width":280,"height":220,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"auth-endpoint-node","type":"text","text":"## 🔐 Authentication\n\n**/login**\n**/logout**\n\n- Bcrypt\n- Session mgmt\n- RBAC","x":180,"y":60,"width":280,"height":220,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"memory-node","type":"text","text":"## 🧠 Memory\n\n**Per-User**\n\nConversation\nBufferMemory\n\nuser_memories{}","x":2940,"y":800,"width":320,"height":240,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"formatter-node","type":"text","text":"## ✏️ Query Formatter\n\n**Optional**\n\ngpt-oss:20b\n\n- Clean queries\n- Normalize text\n- Pre-processing","x":2560,"y":800,"width":320,"height":240,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"active-sessions-node","type":"text","text":"## 📦 ACTIVE_SESSIONS\n\n**In-memory dict**\n\n```python\n{\n  'user': {\n    'last_agent': 'vcenter',\n    'last_agent_time': timestamp,\n    'context': {...}\n  }\n}\n```\n\n3600s timeout","x":2420,"y":1160,"width":520,"height":240,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"sticky-routing-node","type":"text","text":"## 🔄 Sticky Routing\n\n**Conversational Memory**\n\n- Track last_agent per user\n- 180s timeout\n- Auto-route follow-ups\n\n*Ejemplo: \"30 días\" → vCenter*","x":1700,"y":1160,"width":480,"height":240,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"classifier-node","type":"text","text":"## 📌 QueryClassifier\n\n**query_classifier.py**\n\n**4-Layer Decision:**\n0. Exclusive keywords (agents.yaml)\n1. Critical regex patterns\n2. Intent detection (imperative vs question)\n3. Weighted scoring (delta threshold)\n4. LLM fallback + heuristic safety","x":2020,"y":800,"width":480,"height":240,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"embedder-model-node","type":"text","text":"## 📊 Embedding Model\n\n**nomic-embed-text**\n\n- Document embeddings\n- Query embeddings\n- 768 dimensions","x":2370,"y":3940,"width":500,"height":200,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"formatter-model-node","type":"text","text":"## ✨ Formatter Model\n\n**gpt-oss:20b**\n\n- Optional\n- Query cleaning\n- Pre-processing","x":2920,"y":3940,"width":500,"height":200,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"ollama-node","type":"text","text":"## 🧠 Ollama Server\n\n**localhost:11434**\n\n- Local LLM runtime\n- API compatible\n- Model management","x":2920,"y":3600,"width":500,"height":200,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"executor-model-node","type":"text","text":"## 🚀 Executor Model\n\n**gpt-oss:20b**\n\n- Reasoning\n- Tool selection\n- Response generation\n\n**Context:** 8192 tokens","x":2370,"y":3600,"width":500,"height":200,"color":"6"}
